Node.js Demo App with CI/CD Pipeline This is a simple Node.js application deployed using Docker and automated with a CI/CD pipeline using GitHub Actions.

Features Express.js app that returns "Hello from Node.js App!"

Dockerized for containerized deployment

CI/CD pipeline with:

Node.js setup

Install & test steps

Docker image build & push to DockerHub

Project Structure css Copy Edit nodejs-demo-app/ ├── app.js ├── package.json ├── Dockerfile └── .github/ └── workflows/ └── main.yml CI/CD Workflow Triggered on push to the main branch

Builds and tests the app

Builds and pushes Docker image to DockerHub

Run Locally bash Copy Edit npm install node app.js
